<!DOCTYPE html>
<html>
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <title>Your Pooja Has Started</title>
    <style>
        body { font-family: Arial, sans-serif; line-height: 1.6; }
        .container { max-width: 600px; margin: 0 auto; padding: 20px; }
        .header { background-color: #e8f5e9; padding: 20px; text-align: center; }
        .content { padding: 20px; }
        .highlight { background-color: #f1f8e9; padding: 15px; border-left: 4px solid #4CAF50; }
        .footer { margin-top: 20px; padding: 10px; text-align: center; font-size: 12px; color: #777; }
    </style>
</head>
<body>
    <div class="container">
        <div class="header">
            <h2>Your Pooja Has Begun</h2>
        </div>
        
        <div class="content">
            <p>Dear Devotee,</p>
            
            <div class="highlight">
                <p>We're pleased to inform you that <strong><%= panditName %></strong> has started your <strong><%= poojaName %></strong> at <strong><%= startTime %></strong>.</p>
            </div>
            
            <h3>Booking Details:</h3>
            <p><strong>Booking ID:</strong> <%= bookingId %></p>
            <p><strong>Start Time:</strong> <%= startTime %></p>
            
            <p>The sacred rituals are now being performed with devotion for your spiritual benefit.</p>
            
            <p>You will receive another notification when the pooja is completed.</p>
        </div>
        
        <div class="footer">
            <p>May the divine blessings be with you.<br>Â© <%= new Date().getFullYear() %> Vaidic Parampara</p>
        </div>
    </div>
</body>
</html>